      "question": "What are De Morgan\u2019s laws (roughly)?",
      "correctAnswer": "\u00ac(p\u2227q) \u2261 \u00acp\u2228\u00acq and \u00ac(p\u2228q) \u2261 \u00acp\u2227\u00acq",
      "incorrectAnswers": [
        "\u00ac(p\u2227q) \u2261 \u00acp\u2227\u00acq",
        "\u00ac(p\u2228q) \u2261 \u00acp\u2228\u00acq",
        "\u00ac(p\u2192q) \u2261 p\u2192\u00acq"
      ],
      "explanation": "Negation distributes with swapping AND/OR.",
      "keywords": [
        "de-morgan",
        "logic"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/De_Morgan%27s_laws"
    },
